"recBPHeE4vzhLHFDC","ref":"Gen.21.7","text":"And she said, Who would have said unto Abraham, that Sarah should have given children suck? for I have born him a son in his old age."},{"id":"recImVZhtgmF1xDrp","ref":"Gen.21.8","text":"And the child grew, and was weaned: and Abraham made a great feast the same day that Isaac was weaned.","year":-1893}]}
